                                <a href="/Forum/Thread/124">電競滑鼠選購完全指南</a>
                            </h6>
                            <div class="thread-stats">
                                <span><i class="fas fa-eye"></i> 12,890</span>
                                <span><i class="fas fa-comments"></i> 234</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="hot-thread-item">
                        <div class="thread-rank">3</div>
                        <div class="thread-content">
                            <h6>
                                <a href="/Forum/Thread/125">Steam 夏季特賣推薦遊戲</a>
